post.description: Endpoint to import SQL content for initializing or updating the database.

get.description:
Endpoint to create a MySQL database backup by generating SQL statements
for the schema and data, and returning it as a downloadable file.

CPU.title: CPU
CPU.description:
Concrete CPU rows — duplicates ALLOWED (same family+model+speed ok).
Brand-family binding is enforced in the router.

CPUFamily.title: CPUFamily
CPUFamily.description: Family under a brand (e.g., Pentium III, K6-2).

GPU.title: GPU
GPU.description:
Concrete GPU cards — duplicates ALLOWED.
(No uniqueness across model+vram_type+size; manufacturer can vary.)

GPUModel.title: GPUModel
GPUModel.description: Model within a brand (e.g., TNT2 M64, GTX 1080).

GPUVRAMType.title: GPUVRAMType
GPUVRAMType.description: VRAM type (e.g., SDR, DDR, GDDR5, GDDR6).

Motherboard.title: Motherboard
Motherboard.description:
Concrete motherboard rows — duplicates ALLOWED (same model allowed).
Model is free text. FKs required.

MotherboardChipset.title: MotherboardChipset
MotherboardChipset.description: Chipset (e.g., Intel 440BX, AMD B550, VIA KT133).
